{"tid":515433,"cid":17,"subCid":0,"title":"[兩登同步][Live]一月北印度12日遊","createTime":"2017-12-31T12:13:49.000Z","updateTime":"2018-01-12T09:31:49.000Z","uid":78128,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"96902cf77c8ebcf3aec52fe095b7c83a4c590f2a","tid":515433,"uid":78128,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-31T12:13:49.000Z","msg":"之前有篇去Laos Vietnam既爛左尾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n希望今次有恆心打哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n1月5號出發 開定先<br />\n一行二人Backpacking 主要睇歷史遺趾 古堡 探索文化 <br />\n了解印度人既處事態度（有幾差）  當挑戰自己<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n將會去既城市：<br />\nNew Delhi<br />\nJaipur （粉紅色城市）<br />\nJodhpur （藍色城市）<br />\nAmritsar<br />\nAgra<br />\n本來打算去埋Jaisalmer<br />\n但因為火車飛係25號check1月10既飛已經全部變哂waiting list<br />\n同埋車飛都唔平 最後放棄左 選擇搭內陸機由Delhi去Amritsar呢個錫克教城市 來回480一位<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n簡單講下黎緊既plan：<br />\n5號夜晚landing New Delhi<br />\n6號出發去Jaipur會留3日2夜<br />\n大概睇下Hawa Mahal風之宮殿, Nahargarh Fort, Galta Ji<br />\n8號出發去Jodhpur都係3日2夜<br />\n睇Umaid Bhawan Palace, Mehrangarh Fort, Jaswant Thada<br />\n10號搭通宵火車返New Delhi<br />\n11號搭飛機去Amritsar<br />\n睇Wagah Border既印巴士兵降旗禮, Jallianwala Bagh（印度獨立起源地）, Golden Temple<br />\n13號回程 <br />\n14號會係Delhi漫遊 睇下Akshardham 下午17:30會去睇印度超級足球聯賽<br />\nDelhi Dynamos vs Bengaluru FC <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 同當地ultras交流<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n15號去Agra留2日1夜<br />\n睇壓軸戲碼Taj Mahal泰姬陵<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n17號返New Delhi 睇埋餘下既廟<br />\n當晚返香港<br />\n<br />\n暫時budget：<br />\n簽證特區護照USD$50<br />\n機票Airasia來回HKD$2500 不寄倉<br />\n住宿二人房每晚HKD$100-$180 <br />\n火車飛由Cleartrip訂 average 5個鐘車程 冷氣三等床位車廂（一等為頭等） HKD$80 / 1<br />\n冷氣二等床位車廂一倍左右 10個鐘車程 HKD$150 /1<br />\n估計火車一人共耗資 HKD$500<br />\n來陸機New Delhi - Amritsar HKD$480 寄倉 <br />\n市內交通費會call uber／搭tuktuk<br />\n洗費一人預$3000<br />\n估計全個trip一人$7000左右<br />\n<br />\n簽證：<br />\n特區護照evisa USD$50<br />\n本人持有bno 本來諗住用bno簽<br />\n但evisa不接納bno<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\nregular簽證bno唔當香港人身份 打聽過要$1400<br />\n我認衰仔 為左錢認自己係中國香港人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n上佢個visa網online填form 填勁多野 老竇老母職業國籍都要填<br />\n問三代有無巴基斯坦人身份 應該係因為歷史問題<br />\n最後22/12交表 24/12已經approve<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n拍攝工具：<br />\nCannon M3<br />\nI phone SE<br />\nGoPro hero 4 session<br />\n希望拍到d靚相同埋會拍到條好既travel vlog<br />\n影多d古堡靚景<br />\n最期待都係Wagah Border performance同埋Mehrangarh Fort<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/love.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n題外話：<br />\n上面提過會去睇Delhi Dynamos<br />\n所以事前已經inbox左Delhi Dynamos既Ultras<br />\n識左個後生仔 讀緊year2<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n一路向佢打聽住印度同新德里既野 希望黎緊順利d<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n已經約定左佢交換波衫＋頸巾<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />  （我睇香港波）<br />\n<br />\n呢緊幾日諗到有新野會update<br />\n各位有去過印度都可以指導下小弟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n之後就等5號出發<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/kill.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<br />\n整住兩張google既圖頂住先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/31/201259_f516fce01a71703800714438bbe8dfed.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F31%2F201259_f516fce01a71703800714438bbe8dfed.jpg&h=6689cfbe&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nMehrangarh Fort <br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/12/31/201300_810ef0883f56f0f8f29f6f450ac9fefd.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F12%2F31%2F201300_810ef0883f56f0f8f29f6f450ac9fefd.jpg&h=af3e2d95&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\nGolden Temple"},{"pid":"3a0f8d28f47a628ee4fa865b335387f689aee35b","tid":515433,"uid":12865,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-31T12:20:21.000Z","msg":"Lm唔好爛尾啊<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/hoho.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c278c1320105e8a734e03bcabad7b3f6ed616fc1","tid":515433,"uid":68598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-31T12:21:17.000Z","msg":"留名等睇肚痾<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f03c8b46177a71588db90245ecdcd7257a98405f","tid":515433,"uid":78128,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-12-31T12:27:21.000Z","msg":"諗住 講埋疫苗<br />\n11月中睇學校醫生<br />\n醫生建議打兩支<br />\n一支甲肝 一支傷寒<br />\n總共好似＄600<br />\n甲肝當年後要再打一支keep十年 因為暫時呢支只係免疫半年<br />\n傷寒就應該一世 <br />\n其實我唔知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"85e282ddc8ecb72423617f34f9e8775488b1109b","tid":515433,"uid":126038,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-01T14:12:34.000Z","msg":"諗緊二月中去印度 <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e22ad51fdeb9b5c6f007c503e51220d8af99845a","tid":515433,"uid":6833,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c278c1320105e8a734e03bcabad7b3f6ed616fc1","tid":515433,"uid":68598,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2017-12-31T12:21:17.000Z","msg":"留名等睇肚痾<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-01T15:20:03.000Z","msg":"我都驚肚痛<img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5546ee8ed65cbb177bed51d3cbed9e05c541d879","tid":515433,"uid":74792,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2018-01-01T17:01:04.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"cad2c3ea9a5f4ebdd4e285c74137709871807742","tid":515433,"uid":74792,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"201