gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n聽日22:00先land唔知仲有無得兌<br />\nBtw今日深水埗買左電話卡<br />\n$80 4gb 4g 用哂3g無限 無得打電話<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n廢時聽日land左call唔到uber"},{"pid":"720882ba2bae706ccf6305cfbcf637bf1461a9dc","tid":515433,"uid":78128,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-04T21:27:41.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/05/052619_3d8206963756c04c2a1cb92056e5687c.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F05%2F052619_3d8206963756c04c2a1cb92056e5687c.png&h=e285228a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/05/052622_b2bf92c6bb12795df2f1f9a1e26a70ea.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F05%2F052622_b2bf92c6bb12795df2f1f9a1e26a70ea.png&h=c85703e5&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n五點幾先執完行李 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n聽日一點機<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n帶左好撚多對襪<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d036facb0343da185247007f249bf7e27d5ecb42","tid":515433,"uid":81507,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-05T02:53:34.000Z","msg":"Safe flight <img src=\"/assets/faces/xm/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> 等你既遊記"},{"pid":"5bd8dcfcd4705b2066e372dacced9ef7422522ca","tid":515433,"uid":71227,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-01-05T03:42:08.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/05/052619_3d8206963756c04c2a1cb92056e5687c.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2018%2F01%2F05%2F052619_3d8206963756c04c2a1cb92056e5687c.png&h=e285228a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2018/01/05/052622_b2bf92c6bb12795df2f1f9a1e26a70ea.png\